  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter (2 sites) randomized trial evaluating three group treatment models for
      subjects with binge eating disorder. One model is a cognitive behavior treatment (CBT) group,
      one is partial self help, and one is self help only.
    </textblock>
